Transcription.Text: "You mean you gonna tell Mister Carlyle?" Dismounting, Brock slip- knotted the reins around the end post of the hitch rail. "Keep that black devil away from Rusty or you 'll have a sick horse on your hands," he warned, and leaped to the wooden sidewalk.
